lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods said Tuesday he is playing his Hero World Challenge in the Bahamas the first week of December, which would be his first competition in more than 15 months if he follows through with it.

headline.print_headline: Tiger Woods Says He Is Playing in the Bahamas in December
